thread.title: Yalilee Turner

author: Yalilee Turner
title: Yalilee Turner
text: I love one.com because is easy to manage the files on the file manager, and also because If you have a questions the helpdesk answers immediately on a live chat!, not like wix. where you have to find your problem in a forum and try all that, which i hate seriously. so that why I changed from wix.com to one.com because I know if I get in trouble with something I know there is an actual person who is going to answer my questions on a live chat.
